/**
 * Poker - 5 Card Draw
 *
 * Authors: Alexander Nichols, Evan Tyra, Daniel Bond, Michael Bjorge
 * ECE 373 : Software (Intensive) Engineering
 * Fall 2013
 */

To build the poker executable, just run make in the base directory.

To run the game, just run ./poker

The game is standard 5 card draw poker. You play against 3 computer players. You are given a set amount of money at the start. If at any point you are unable to make the minimum ante to play, you are kicked out.

Stubs, drivers, and test suits are in the /tests folder

Class diagrams, the requirements document, initial class diagrams, and the contract are the in the /documentation folder
